<H3> <TI>   Military Said To Destroy 38 Armenian `Chemical Projectiles' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2602165694 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network in Azeri 0930 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2602165694 </F>
<F P=104>  Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Azeri </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Azerbaijan has disclosed that the Azerbaijan 
military forces have destroyed 38 chemical projectiles since the 
beginning of the clashes in Karabakh. The projectiles were 
fired by the Armenian military forces against the northern part 
of Karabakh. 

</TEXT>

