<H3> <TI>   Abkhaz Official on Russian-Georgian Treaty </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2702095594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0700 GMT 
27 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2702095594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vladislav Ardzinba, the Supreme Soviet chairman of 
Abkhazia, has expressed his fear that the realization of 
documents on the Russian-Georgian Treaty on Friendship and 
Cooperation which was signed would start, irrespective of the 
ratification of this treaty. Ardzinba underlined that he has 
already received information that the fulfillment of these 
documents has in fact started. 

</TEXT>

