<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Moscow February 25 TASS -- President Boris Yeltsin 
appointed Sergey Tsiplyayev his plenipotentiary representative 
at the Interparliamentary Assembly of the Commonwealth of 
Independent States. 
  Yeltsin's decree notes that the appointment was prompted by 
the need for maintaining permanent relations between the Russian 
president and the Interparliamentary Assembly of the CIS states. 
