<H3> <TI>   Kravchuk Meets Mitterrand's Representative </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  WS0103102794 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 0600 GMT 1 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0103102794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yesterday, President Leonid Kravchuk received Ms. 
(Anne Leuvergaunt), personal representative of French President 
Francois Mitterand. The visit came as a result of a recent 
telephone conversation between the Ukrainian and French 
presidents. Its purpose is to determine specific programs of 
