<F P=102>  LD0103152994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1400 GMT 
1 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0103152994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Today at the court session on the case of the SCSE 
[State Committee for the State of Emergency] in the military 
collegium of the Russian Supreme Court, a decision was reached 
in accordance with which the criminal proceedings against the 
defendants Anatoliy Lukyanov, Valentin Pavlov, Vladimir 
Kryuchkov, Oleg Shenin, Dmitriy Yazov, Oleg Baklanov, Valentin 
Varennikov, Yuriy Plekhanov, Vyacheslav Generalov, Aleksandr 
Tizyakov, and Vasiliy Starodubtsev were halted. This decision 
was taken by the court after the defendants had expressed 
agreement with the resolution on the amnesty adopted on 23 
February in the State Duma and had called for a complete stop to 
the judicial examination. 

