<H3> <TI>   Rybkin To Join Presidential Council </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0103140794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1340 
GMT 1 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0103140794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] </F>
  [Text] Moscow, 1 Mar -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin 
issued a resolution today to make Ivan Rybkin, chairman of the 
State Duma, an additional member of the Presidential Council for 
personnel policy. This was announced today by the press service 
of the Russian president. 

</TEXT>

