<F P=102>  LD0103144594 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 1200 
GMT 1 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0103144594 </F>
<F P=104>  Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Tajik </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Imamali Rakhmanov, head of state and chairman of the 
Supreme Council of the Republic of Tajikistan, has just received 
Russian Deputy Foreign Minister Anatoliy Adamishin. The meeting 
