<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Azeri </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A press conference has been held in the Azerbaijan 
Ministry of Foreign Affairs on the outcome of President Geydar 
Aliyev's visit to Britain. The press conference was held for 
foreign and local journalists. President Aliyev said that 
several important documents were signed during his visit and 
that the agreements between Azerbaijan and Britain will create a 
