currently visiting Bonn. The itinerary for his visit includes 
talks with Foreign Minister Klaus Kinkel, a visit to the German 
Bundestag, and talks with Minister of Economic Cooperation 
Carl-Dieter Spranger and representatives of Germany's business 
circles. 

