<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Baku (March 1) TURAN--As was reported earlier, local 
police blockaded the building of Baku-based TURAN NEWS AGENCY. 
  Due to this fact, our agency is unable to function. The 
building is searched without the sanctions of the Procurator. 
The police does not explain the reasons of their activities. 
  The Ministry of Internal Affairs of Azerbaijan, Procurator's 
Office and President's staff of the Republic give no details 
about present situation and refuse to answer the question of the 
journalists. Presently we use several additional sources to 
inform you about the situation. 

